<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/6c09200ba1ba4375a7c6aba91e102a13.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">别问我哪里还有</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201205/8f0dbdeb5d604ade97e0572e3e5ec97d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>张牙舞爪，下锅前还在扭！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201205/92b5115b26414882b9831c381d4cfbb5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201205/ce78088a8479425cb5fee910f3229659.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201205/285db476e3724ce884ce2b655388b577.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">终于被我发现了！公园前这家韩料店，有韩综同款的<strong>活章鱼料理！</strong>前一秒还<strong>张牙舞爪</strong>，下一秒就要下锅噜~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/e9ecda949b7b49858014d8035270aa53.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/c217f9e1485d48e3b165d5499e0e915c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">清理干净后，就...<strong>整只直接下锅</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>这么大只，咋吃啊！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/19612a6e3f3e40aea87485e8e09d9acf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/674c9947bfdd4bac9f30eb3d64e247e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">煮沸没多久，大章鱼就变得通红发亮，几乎<strong>霸占了整口锅</strong>！一下子竟不知道从哪里下口...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/be4847531ec3474eb31a8aa689fc99e5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/f186160ca9294902812030444b5e3a8f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">煮熟的须须弹性十足，有<strong>两根手指这么粗</strong>！光一条就能霸占整个屏幕，好想咬一口...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201205/febf3d2f27ec48d69a4ffe6197a2cb33.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201205/9ed22e26ffa3478d80f8060fb2397d10.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201205/da357e82f4cd4557bd48ccfba2fe4fe7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">别急！店员小哥会帮忙<strong>剪成小粒粒</strong>，可以先吃几口感受章鱼哥的弹嫩，也可以再煮多几分钟，让<strong>汤汁更鲜，更入味！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201205/9baa1f1017b945b8bf1d04e413b43f13.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201205/050c3dd13c064c67ad43c32fddeec09e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有板烧和冰镇可选，不会动得那么厉害～</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>板烧活八爪鱼，有两个版本</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/04652b0c1a6548cea5b6142b69da48bd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>白烧or红酱</strong>，店内都可以做！想更好感受新鲜章鱼肉质的鲜甜，我建议白烧～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/7397407017a247c3abf5d596589dc799.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201205/cfbbe387d61445b385b2025d12a2270c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201205/bde30d290f0b4261a554127d1b956248.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">同样是一整只章鱼开烧！考虑到板板比较小，一次先烤四五条须须。有<strong>三种蘸酱</strong>可选，我推荐甜辣酱！焦香鲜甜，我一口气吃光了一整盘！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>冰镇活八爪鱼，我真香了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/48f0c42fe85a4177aaa05dfacc226aed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“冷静”下来的章鱼哥</strong>，直接剪着吃！讲真，见识过TA张牙舞爪，一开始我是拒绝的･̆-･̆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/b04bbe30c19f4adb87c69206c66c8552.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/6dad34a2ee2c49f7993a6a7bdcffe7e5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在朋友威逼利诱下尝了一口，结果我<strong>真香</strong>了！调制的酱汁极大地激发出鲜味，真的一点也不腥！<strong>Q弹爽滑，完全停不下嘴...</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201215/68e02f09f42e45d1bb9900cf057f830c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201215/f12833967a314196b4baadb078218053.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201205/81ba2de2ab4b4ce5b8e6a442d72a5e89.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/6ab1583986c44c4dbf9c1fbf29ef11d9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">吃个大章鱼就满足啦？店里还有超多<strong>超正宗的韩料</strong>呢！据说厨师长是<strong>朝鲜族的欧巴</strong>哦～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/c820948e87e04677ae378ee88408cbfe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">特别是五味炸鸡，酥酥脆脆端上来立马被抢光光！蜂蜜芥末、芝士、甜辣…像我这么贪心的人，当然每种都要尝一口～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201205/b08bc071ee0f421ba27b3cfd0f971a87.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/6bcbf112d4224a68a62cecbe21baa1c5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201205/cf9b1ea2d3f44cc985d9c863af1607be.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有<strong>自己DIY的手工饭团、糖渍冰番茄、豆浆冷面</strong>...看起来简单，吃一口就知道大有来头～</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>04</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201205/db9eac4eaec9417fa4add408beee1dc0.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201205/b2a00dad6d71479e99edccd66967817b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/462116ea882240e88bcc9fb31e33de7d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“所以，在哪里可以吃到呢？”不卖关子啦，这家店开在<strong>惠福东路</strong>，你一眼就能认出TA：怎么把韩国<strong>街头小饭店</strong>搬来了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">💫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201205/1610bcc36ad948dda4ef523ed7ecc365.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">就算是工作日，店里也坐得<strong>满满当当</strong>，顺便一提：店员小哥都是<strong>韩系帅哥</strong>喔！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/e7f6dba26c554d80ad8573232d890a7b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">💞💞💞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201205/d4b721b34a274aa889d3a353a7332a00.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201205/92f35bd8de474268a517e06b6028e93b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">😲😲😲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/f0b0a504f03f4ed3bce3ad5e71341026.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">清酒摆了满墙，韩剧里的铁皮桌椅、霓虹灯... 发到朋友圈都问我<strong>是不是去韩国了</strong>！还原度也太高了吧~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201205/e81be1d5cc2c498ab714996f6357d297.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店名也很好记，跟我一起念哦：<strong>咬米咬米，yummy yummy～</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
